        <docPara content='This+example+is+another+spin+on+the+classic+hello+world+example.+The%0A++application+allocates+a+buffer+and+passes+the+buffer%27s+base+address%0A++to+a+kernel+running+on+the+compute+device.+The+kernel+function+writes%0A++the+string+%22Hello+World%22+into+the+buffer.+The+application+then+reads%0A++the+string+from+the+buffer.'/>
