        <docPara content='Edit+the+project+makefile+to+update+the+product+variables.+They+are+at%0A++the+top+of+the+makefile.+You+need+to+replace+the+text+%3Ctt%3Eyour_version_number%3C%2Ftt%3E%0A++with+the+actual+product+version+which+is+installed.+For+example%2C+the%0A++XDCtools+variable+might+look+like+this.'/>
