        <docPara content='To+modify+the+memory+map%2C+edit+the+%3Ctt%3Econfig.bld%3C%2Ftt%3E+file.+Note%3A+the+first%0A++time+you+edit+this+file%2C+you+must+associate+the+XDCscript+editor+with%0A++this+file.+Do+this+for+both+%3Ctt%3E*.bld%3C%2Ftt%3E+and+%3Ctt%3E*.cfg%3C%2Ftt%3E+files.+Subsequently%2C%0A++you+will+be+able+to+just+double-click+the+file+to+edit+it.'/>
        <docPara content='%3CUL%3E%3CLI%3E+Select+config.bld%0A%3C%2FLI%3E%3CLI%3E+Right-Mouse-Button+%26gt%3B+Open+With+%26gt%3B+XDCscript+Editor%0A%3C%2FLI%3E%3C%2FUL%3E'/>
        <docPara content='The+variable+%3Ctt%3EMemMapSects%3C%2Ftt%3E+defines+all+the+memory+map+sections+and%0A++their+properties.+You+can+modify%2C+add%2C+or+remove+these+as+needed+for%0A++your+executable.+Use+the+comment+at+the+top+of+the+file+to+help+keep%0A++track+of+your+memory+map.+See+the+xdc.platform.IPlatform+documentation%0A++for+a+description+of+the+memory+map+section.+Each+memory+map+section+is%0A++of+type+%3Ctt%3Emetaonly+struct+Memory%3C%2Ftt%3E+defined+in+the+documentation.'/>
        <docPara content='Edit+your+linker+command+files+from+your+host+and+device+projects.+Look%0A++for+the+%3Ctt%3EMEMORY%3C%2Ftt%3E+directive.+Using+the+memory+sections+defined+in+your%0A++linker+command+file%2C+create+similar+sections+in+the+MemMapSects+object.%0A++Delete+any+unused+sections.'/>
