        <docPara content='Note+that+program+code+and+data+sections+have+names+to+reflect+which%0A++core+they+apply+to+%28e.g.+CODE_DSP%2C+CODE_T16%29.+The+DMEM+section+is+slightly%0A++smaller+to+accomodate+the+SharedRegion_0+section.+The+SharedRegion_0%0A++memory+section+replaces+the+KARG+memory+section.+It+is+used+by+the+OpenCL%0A++implementation+for+passing+kernel+function+arguments.+The+VECS+section%0A++is+required+by+SYS%2FBIOS.'/>
